high_descs: Turn around and go forward, then turn left to go to the sink.
Pick up the potato from the right sink basin.
Turn around and step forward, then turn left to go to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the potato inside and heat it up, then take the potato out.
Turn around and step forward, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the potato in the right sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm potato in the sink.

high_descs: Turn the opposite direction and go along the counter to your left to the right side of the sink.
Get the potato from the sink.
Carry the potato to the microwave on your right.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Carry the potato back to the sink.
Put the potato back in the right side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato in a kitchen sink.

high_descs: Turn and go to the sink.
Pick up a potato in the sink.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Turn and go to the  sink.
Put the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved potato in the sink.
